---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("August 3 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Find the Right Bi-Weekly Cleaner Nashville"
  description={isPublished ? "Full Article: Reclaiming Your Weekends: Finding the Right Bi-Weekly Cleaner in Nashville" : "Coming Soon: Reclaiming Your Weekends: Finding the Right Bi-Weekly Cleaner in Nashville"}
  noindex={!isPublished}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Reclaiming Your Weekends: Finding the Right Bi-Weekly Cleaner in Nashville"
    description="Stop spending weekends cleaning! Learn how to find the right bi-weekly house cleaner in Nashville so you can reclaim your free time and enjoy the city."
    publishDate="August 3 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Value/Time-Saving
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Reclaiming Your Weekends: Finding the Right Bi-Weekly Cleaner in Nashville
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming August 3 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>August 3 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>How Can You Reclaim Your Weekends with a Bi-Weekly Cleaner in Nashville?</h2>
<p><strong>Reclaiming your weekends starts with choosing the right bi-weekly cleaning service. A professional service like The Valley Clean Team offers systematic and precise cleaning, allowing you to enjoy your free time without stress. With transparent pricing and guaranteed satisfaction, investing in a bi-weekly cleaner is a step towards a more balanced life.</strong></p>

<h3>Why Choose a Bi-Weekly Cleaning Service?</h3>
<p>In Nashville's bustling environment, time is your most valuable asset. Managing work, family, and social commitments can leave little room for maintaining a spotless home. A bi-weekly cleaning service offers:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Consistent Cleanliness:</strong> Regular visits ensure your home remains inviting without the hassle.</li>
  <li><strong>Time Savings:</strong> Spend your weekends enjoying Nashville, not scrubbing floors.</li>
  <li><strong>Professional Expertise:</strong> Our trained cleaning specialists execute with military precision.</li>
</ul>

<h4>What to Look for in a Cleaning Service</h4>
<p>Not all cleaning services are created equal. To ensure you’re making a wise investment, consider these factors:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Reputation:</strong> Look for services with positive reviews and a strong community presence in Nashville.</li>
  <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Choose a company that offers upfront pricing without hidden costs.</li>
  <li><strong>Guarantees:</strong> Opt for a service that stands behind their work with a satisfaction guarantee.</li>
</ul>

<h3>The Valley Clean Team Difference</h3>
<p>As a veteran-owned and operated business, The Valley Clean Team brings unparalleled precision and accountability to every cleaning appointment. Our presence in the Nashville community underscores our commitment to quality and integrity.</p>

<h4>Our Systematic Approach</h4>
<p>We employ standard operating procedures (SOPs) to ensure every corner of your home is meticulously cleaned. Our process includes:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Vetted Specialists:</strong> Each team member undergoes thorough training and background checks.</li>
  <li><strong>Military-Precision Checklists:</strong> Our systematic approach guarantees nothing is overlooked.</li>
  <li><strong>Customizable Plans:</strong> Tailor your cleaning services to fit your unique needs.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Experience the Benefits of a Guaranteed Clean</h3>
<p>Imagine weekends spent exploring Nashville's vibrant culture or simply relaxing at home, knowing your cleaning needs are covered. With The Valley Clean Team, you can stop worrying about housework and focus on what truly matters.</p>

<h4>Transparent Pricing</h4>
<p>We offer transparent pricing starting at $125, with no unexpected fees. Compare our offerings, and you'll see how we provide unmatched value.</p>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time: Book Your Guaranteed Clean with The Valley Clean Team Today</h3>
<p>Your time is precious, and your home deserves the best. The Valley Clean Team provides a reliable, premium cleaning service tailored to your needs. Reclaim your weekends and enjoy peace of mind with our expert solutions. <strong>Book your bi-weekly cleaning service now and experience the difference.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">August 3 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
